{"tid":137240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"投資者財困蝕賣大埔比華利山    6年貶805萬","createTime":"2017-02-27T16:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T10:55:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73bc793d735bac1dfb2fef14aec04e63a10bd9f6","tid":137240,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/大埔比華利山-6年貶805萬-225520180--sector.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E6%AF%94%E8%8F%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%B1%B1-6%E5%B9%B4%E8%B2%B6805%E8%90%AC-225520180--sector.html&d=IcHW%2FfQ2zQNJFdNzTrXWKMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ceccecb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/大埔比華利山-6年貶805萬-225520180--sector.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/hket/HKET_20170224_D03_01_a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fhket%2FHKET_20170224_D03_01_a.jpg&h=d8c7c0ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【經濟日報專訊】投資者財困，市場連錄數宗蝕讓個案。大埔比華利山別墅再錄蝕讓個案，昨日由銀主身份以2,280萬元售出，單位6年間帳面貶值805萬元。<br />\n<br />\n涉及物業愛琴道單號屋，實用面積2,075平方呎，原業主於2011年中以約3,085萬元購入，曾向財務公司承借二按，及後被財務公司沒收業權，昨以2,280萬元售出，單位6年間帳面貶值805萬元，若連釐印費等支出，估計原業主要蝕讓逾940萬元。<br />\n<br />\n世紀21灝天地產董事盧嘉麟指出，日前有內地投資者大幅減價放售比華利山別墅數個單位，上述買家最終選擇樓齡新的愛琴道大屋。<br />\n<br />\n其次，市場消息透露，東涌海堤灣畔3座高層H室，實用面積562平方呎，屬於兩房間隔，原業主為內地客，於2014年9月以約538萬元購入單位，原本一直用作收租，惟近日財政出現困難，於是以低價5%推出市場放售，最終以610萬元易手，帳面獲利72萬元。惟持貨不足3年，是次易手須繳交10%（61萬元）額外印花稅（SSD），若連釐印費及代理佣金等支出，實質蝕讓約20萬元離場。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣環宇海灣1100萬 明賺暗蝕<br />\n<br />\n另外，土地註冊處資料顯示，荃灣環宇海灣6座高層F室，實用面積898平方呎，原業主2014年7月以1,065萬元購入，剛以1,100萬元易手，帳面獲利35萬元。惟持貨不足3年，同樣涉及10%額外印花稅，估計業主實質蝕讓逾百萬元。<br />\n<br />\n其次，柴灣灣景園高層G室，實用面積624平方呎，2013年以696萬購入，以725萬易手，帳面獲利26萬元，扣除雜項支出明賺暗蝕。"},{"pid":"42270f1f35588364ebfb5049782c2fd003c887a2","tid":137240,"uid":592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T20:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常買得house 都係自住多"},{"pid":"dea4d0638cc485cf9d9852673e472b6f33655265","tid":137240,"uid":17174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T20:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常買得house 都係自住多</blockquote><br />\n比華利山買黎自住既得三成左右"},{"pid":"d9a7f5bbde003077585275f15915a03e035d0170","tid":137240,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb1a924eb6eebc665a65fa4e18aafb0df2c7e99","tid":137240,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"東涌&hellip;六百個!?"},{"pid":"dae255efed28c2ae130a3026e852abd39a90f8bd","tid":137240,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T01:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東涌&hellip;六百個!?</blockquote><br />\n有鐵路直出中環"},{"pid":"4a60466236f907d45a1e2c5a070446ed44aaab7b","tid":137240,"uid":34184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東涌&hellip;六百個!?</blockquote><br />\n機師/溝空姐用<br />\n<br />\n同都叫海境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573c2d05de08f7cc752e919d72396b85eb7a1331","tid":137240,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"好奇怪,8-10年前買既1-2千萬新派豪宅 ,全部冇升過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5462b8228928af63333aadb43608c9144e57847","tid":137240,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"變左銀主盤喎, 個原業主本身無錢供 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586dfab7146a524bfa1dd73208ac9346f34d9195","tid":137240,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f347ae74e6f1f88db7cb45edea6bb11b1